more Inazuma Eleven Go Galaxy introduces Football Frontier International Vision 2 (FFIV2) with Shinsei Inazuma Japan as the protagonist team. The team includes previous characters such as Matsukaze Tenma, Shindou Takuto, and Tsurugi Kyousuke, as well as other new characters, all who are known to be talented in fields such as boxing, mathematics, and rhythmic gymnastics, but poor at soccer.
